1. Your system needs to run Python3 in order to execute the code.
2. To run the code, change directory to Assignment1-Indexer/src.
3. Run using $python Indexer.py <pathToCollectionFile> <0/1>
	The 1 or 0 value specifies whether compression is performed or not respectively.
4. All generated indices, lookup and mappings can be found in the data directory.